msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/complete"
msgid ""
"Congratulations, you have finished the fourth tutorial (Reinforcements)."
msgstr "Enhorabuena, has terminado el cuarto tutorial (Refuerzos)."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/date"
msgid "June 25nd, 1941 · Border with the USSR"
msgstr "25 de junio de 1941 - Frontera con la URSS"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint_video"
msgid "Press this button to re-watch the video for this tutorial phase."
msgstr "Pulsa este botón para volver a ver el vídeo de esta fase del tutorial."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/name"
msgid "Tutorial 4: Reinforcements"
msgstr "Tutorial 4: Refuerzos"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/name_big"
msgid "Reinforcements"
msgstr "Refuerzos"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/00"
msgid ""
"Soldaten! Welcome back to the front line! Today you will learn advanced "
"strategies like requesting reinforcements from HQ and using support weaponry "
"like the artillery signaller."
msgstr ""
"¡Soldados! ¡Bienvenidos de nuevo al frente! Hoy aprenderéis estrategias "
"avanzadas como solicitar refuerzos al Cuartel General y utilizar armamento "
"de apoyo, como puede ser el señalizador de artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/00a"
msgid ""
"First, call in a 'Rifle Squad'. Once they arrive, order them into the "
"trenches."
msgstr ""
"Primero, llama a una \"Escuadra de Fusileros\". Cuando lleguen, ordénales "
"que vayan a las trincheras."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/00c"
msgid "Excellent! New units are available to reinforce your defenses!"
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente! ¡Hay nuevas unidades disponibles para reforzar tus defensas!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint/reinf_info4"
msgid ""
"When you hover your cursor over each reinforcement button you will see "
"additional information."
msgstr ""
"Cuando pases el cursor por encima de cada botón de refuerzo, verás "
"información adicional."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint/reinf_info5"
msgid ""
"Currently, the Manpower points (MP) available to you are limited, but there "
"is enough for you to call in the required units. Depending on the situation, "
"additional points may be awarded for completing objectives."
msgstr ""
"Actualmente, los puntos de material (MP) de que dispones son limitados, pero "
"hay suficientes para que puedas comprar las unidades necesarias. Durante las "
"misiones, se conceden puntos adicionales al¡ completar objetivos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/01"
msgid ""
"Now, call in a MG 34, a 8cm mortar, and a 2cm Flak. Place them on the "
"frontline to defend our HQ."
msgstr ""
"Ahora, solicita un Lafette MG 34, un 8cm sGrW 34 y un 2cm FlaK 30. Colócalos "
"en primera línea para defender nuestro Cuartel General."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/02"
msgid ""
"Prepare your units to defend the front line. Our scouts provided an "
"estimated time before the enemy attack will arrive."
msgstr ""
"Prepara a tus unidades para defender la línea del frente. Nuestros "
"exploradores nos informan del tiempo estimado antes de que llegue el ataque "
"enemigo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint/skiphelp"
msgid ""
"A new reinforcement option is unlocked: 'Skip preparation phase'. It will "
"allow you to skip the current preparation phase and begin the next phase. "
"Often it is the enemy attack."
msgstr ""
"Ahora tienes un nuevo botón en los refuerzos: \"Saltar fase preparación\". "
"Te permitirá saltarte el temporizador actual y comenzar la siguiente fase de "
"la misión. A menudo se trata de saltar directamente al ataque enemigo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint/artyzone"
msgid ""
"You must call artillery on the active battlefield of the map to complete its "
"task."
msgstr ""
"Debes solicitar un ataque de artillería en la zona enemiga para completar el "
"objetivo."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/hint/"
"airstrikezone"
msgid ""
"You must call the target area within the map borders for the air strike to "
"complete it's task."
msgstr ""
"Debes indicar dónde se debe realizar el ataque aéreo, por la zona enemiga, "
"para completer la tarea."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/03"
msgid ""
"Good job, they are running away! Your next objective is to call in an "
"Artillery Signaller."
msgstr ""
"Buen trabajo, ¡están huyendo! Tu siguiente objetivo es solicitar que nos "
"refuerzen con un Señalizador de Artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/03b"
msgid ""
"Crawl to approach the enemy outpost undetected, then signal for an artillery "
"bombardment by firing a flare with your flare pistol."
msgstr ""
"Arrástrate para acercarte al puesto avanzado enemigo sin ser detectado, y "
"luego dispara una bengala sobre el objetivo enemigo para iniciar el "
"bombardeo de artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/04"
msgid "Excellent work! Now we must destroy the enemy and capture their HQ."
msgstr ""
"¡Excelente trabajo! Ahora debemos destruir al enemigo y capturar su Cuartel "
"General."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/04b"
msgid ""
"You now have additional units and resources available to call in for "
"reinforcements."
msgstr ""
"Ahora dispones de unidades y recursos adicionales para pedir refuerzos."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/05a"
msgid "Airstrikes and artillery strikes are now available to be called in."
msgstr "Ahora se pueden convocar ataques aéreos y de artillería."

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/05b"
msgid ""
"Your orders are to attack the enemy with both air and artillery strikes!"
msgstr "Tus órdenes son atacar al enemigo con ataques aéreos y de artillería"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/05c"
msgid ""
"Intelligence suggests Russians have a heavy tank at their HQ. An airstrike "
"would be most effective to deal with that problem!"
msgstr ""
"Los servicios de inteligencia sugieren que los rusos tienen un tanque pesado "
"en su cuartel general. Un ataque aéreo sería lo más eficaz para resolver "
"este pequeño problema"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/reinf_arrive"
msgid "Reinforcements are here!"
msgstr "¡Ya están aquí los refuerzos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/narrator/"
"ger_officer/reinf_arrive_alt"
msgid "Reinforcements have arrived!"
msgstr "¡Los refuerzos han llegado!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/timer"
msgid "Prepare to defend the frontline"
msgstr "Prepárate para defender la primera línea"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/skiphint"
msgid "Skip the preparation phase when you’re ready!"
msgstr "¡Sáltate la fase de preparación cuando estés preparado!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/defendstatus"
msgid "Repel the enemy attack"
msgstr "Repele el ataque enemigo"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/outro_completed"
msgid ""
"Mission Accomplished!\n"
"\n"
"Click on 'continue' to keep playing this mission or click on 'next' to "
"proceed directly into the next mission."
msgstr ""
"¡Misión cumplida!\n"
"\n"
"Haz clic en \"Continuar\" para seguir jugando esta misión o en \"Siguiente\" "
"para pasar directamente a la siguiente misión."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/place"
msgid "Army Group Centre"
msgstr "Grupo de Ejércitos Centro"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/replay_video"
msgid "Replay Video"
msgstr "Repetir el video"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/story"
msgid ""
"Welcome to support weaponry training, Soldier.\n"
"\n"
"In this tutorial, you will learn the basics of reinforcements. This includes "
"calling in additional standard units and requesting support assets such as "
"artillery and air strikes.\n"
"\n"
"                                      Good luck!"
msgstr ""
"Bienvenido al entrenamiento con armas de apoyo, soldado.\n"
"\n"
"En este tutorial, aprenderás a solicitar refuerzos. Esto incluye a unidades "
"estándar y tambien solicitar recursos de apoyo como artillería y ataques "
"aéreos.\n"
"\n"
"                                      ¡Mucha suerte!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task0"
msgid "Call in the Rifle Squad and move them into the trenches!"
msgstr "¡Adquiere un Escuadrón de Fusileros y llévalos a las trincheras!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task1"
msgid ""
"Call in a MG 34, a 8cm Mortar and a 2cm Flak. Place them on the frontline "
"(green outline) to defend our HQ!"
msgstr ""
"Adquiere un Lafette MG 34, un 8cm sGrW 34 y un 2cm FlaK 30. ¡Colócalos en la "
"primera línea (contorno verde) para defender nuestro Cuartel General!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task2"
msgid "Skip Preparation Phase."
msgstr "Sáltate la Fase de Preparación."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task3"
msgid "Call in the Artillery Signaller!"
msgstr "¡Adquiere un Señalizador de Artillería!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task4"
msgid "Carefully advance towards - and shoot a flare at - the enemy outpost!"
msgstr "Avanza con cuidado hacia el puesto enemigo y dispara una bengala."

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task5"
msgid "Capture the enemy HQ"
msgstr "Captura el cuartel general enemigo"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task6"
msgid "Call off-map Airstrike on enemy targets!"
msgstr "¡Convoca un Ataque Aéreo sobre objetivos enemigos!"

msgctxt "mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/task7"
msgid "Call off-map Artillery on enemy targets!"
msgstr "¡Solicita un bombardeo de artillería contra los objetivos enemigos!"

msgctxt ""
"mission/single/00-bootcamp/04_reinforcements-offmap-support/outro_failed"
msgid "You have been defeated!"
msgstr "¡Has sido derrotado!"

